flowchart TD

    A[Application Launch] --> B[Initialize JavaFX Stage]
    B --> C[Create Board Model]
    C --> D[Place Mines]
    D --> E[Calculate Adjacent Counts]
    E --> F[Create UI Grid]
    F --> G[Display Scene]

    G --> H{User Clicks Cell}

    H --> I{Left Click or Right Click}

    I -- Left Click --> J[Reveal Selected Cell]
    I -- Right Click --> K[Toggle Flag State]

    K --> L[Update UI Cell Appearance]
    L --> H

    J --> M{Cell Is Mine}

    M -- Yes --> N[Reveal All Mines]
    N --> O[Display Game Over Message]
    O --> P{Restart Game}

    P -- Yes --> C
    P -- No --> Q[End Application]

    M -- No --> R{Adjacent Count Is Zero}

    R -- Yes --> S[Reveal Neighbor Cells Recursively]
    S --> T[Update UI Grid]

    R -- No --> T

    T --> U{All Safe Cells Revealed}

    U -- Yes --> V[Display Win Message]
    V --> P

    U -- No --> H